{"tid":2081799,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[Mike Orange] 《歎息橋》原聲大碟演奏會","createTime":"2020-06-27T13:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T13:32:46.000Z","uid":353175,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd42791ccb1c098a79ee9613699a3a166690d1d8","tid":2081799,"uid":353175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:32:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">睇歎息橋嗰時已經好鍾意Mike啲配樂<br />\n佢竟然仲為隻OST開演奏會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想聽到Yours Truly 現場版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4pDo5G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4pDo5G.jpg&h=bcb6be84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMike Orange將聯同樂手們現場演繹《歎息橋》原聲大碟內的曲目，以及部分沒收錄在專輯內的配樂曲目。電視劇《歎息橋》是這一系列配樂誕生的起點，然而我們相信每一個樂章都有其獨特的氛圍和想像；希望透過是次演奏會，在沒有畫面和劇情的導向下，為這系列曲目賦予新的生命，期望那份純粹的創造力會為大家帶來不一樣的體驗。"}]}